'''1FLTV''' ''(1 Fürstentum Liechtenstein Television)''<ref>[http://www.1fl.li/about].  1FLTV.</ref> is [[Liechtenstein]]'s first television broadcaster. It began operation on 15 August 2008 in the [[German language]].

==History==

On 15 August 2008, 1FLTV began operation after being licensed by the Liechtenstein government.<ref name=esc824>{{cite web|url=http://www.esctoday.com/news/read/12220|title=Liechtenstein Gets a TV Station|last=Kuipers|first=Michael|date= 24 August 2008|publisher=ESCToday|accessdate= 24 August 2008|archivedate=25 August 2008|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080825081712/http://www.esctoday.com/news/read/12220}}</ref> It broadcasts in German and is a business venture of [[Austrians|Austrian]] businesswoman [[Beatrix Schartl]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sdtv.gr/news-2950.html|title='1 FL TV', το πρώτο ιδιωτικό κανάλι στο Λίχτενσταϊν|date= 19 August 2008|work= sdtv.gr|language=Greek |accessdate= 24 August 2008| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080912155913/http://www.sdtv.gr/news-2950.html| archivedate= 12 September 2008 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>

