| released       = {{Film date|2011|12|13}}
| runtime        = 68 minutes
| language       = [[Estonian language|Estonian]], [[Armenian language|Armenian]], [[Russian language|Russian]], [[Turkish language|Turkish]], [[Kurdish language|Kurdish]]
